6. Hello, my name is Andrey. I work as a computer repairer and software tuner. I go to people's homes and help them solve their computer problems. We call it emergency computer help. This job brings in very little money. In my free time, I participate in ambassador programs and incentivized testnets of various blockchain projects. Here are some projects I've been involved with NuCypher, Harmony, Avalanche, Elrond, Solana, Stafi, CertiK, XX network, Akash, Mina, Blockstack, Keep, Bitsong, Mina. I accumulated several years of rewards from these events, saved for my retirement and hoped to buy a house. I am already 41 years old. I have a wife and two children aged 7 and 9. We live in Ukraine, the city of Dnipro. So far, we are relatively calm, not like in Mariupol or Kharkov. But the wife and children are very afraid, several times war plane flew right overhead at a low altitude, rocket explosions have so far only been heard. My wife is afraid to leave Ukraine without me, we were preparing to go abroad all together, I am not fit for military service even in wartime and we should be released. We need this money now more than ever. I really hope for your understanding of my situation. I myself never took anything from someone else, even the phones that I found more than once always returned to the owners. Thank you in advance. I apologize for my English, I used google translate.
